author: wn.com
title: Open government groups to meet with administration officials
text: PROVIDENCE, R.I. (AP) - Five organizations that have raised concerns about the administration's commitment to the public's right to know are meeting with state officials. ACCESS/RI, American Civil Liberties Union, Rhode Island Press Association, New England First Amendment Coalition and League of Women Voters were invited to the statehouse Tuesday. ... ...
